          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Interface2">X </text>and<text styleclass="Interface2"> Y-axes</text> of a <text styleclass="Element">Part</text> also have their own <text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">coordinate-system! They are similar to Lines.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The bottom image to the left shows the Coordinate-System of the </text><text styleclass="Interface2">Y-</text><text styleclass="VariableName">axis</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">local</text> +<text styleclass="VariableName">x-axis</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Y-axis</text> of a <text styleclass="Element">Part</text> is along the <text styleclass="VariableName">Y-axis</text>!</para>
